Package com.brogrammers.agora.views

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnswerActivity
    Answer Activity which displays the view of answers corresponding to a question.
    AnswerAdapter
    Adapter required to format answers from a question to the answerActivity of the question.
    AuthorAnswerActivity
    Activity screen when posting an answer to a question.
    AuthorQuestionActivity
    Activity for posting a question to the app.
    CommentActivity
    Comment activity for displaying a list of comments corresponding to a question/answer.
    CommentAdapter
    Adapter for populating and formatting comments onto comment view
    MainActivity
    Main view of the Agora app.
    QuestionActivity
    Question activity displaying view of a single question.
    QuestionAdapter
    Question adapter is required to assemble the question object for the UI implementation.
    SearchActivity
    Activity(View) to display search results Contains two fragments: one to show answers and one the show answers
    SearchActivity.AnswersFragment
    A fragment containing a list of Questions from the search results
